                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[02.09.2010]</p>
                <p>– The European Year for Combating Poverty and Social Exclusion 2010 is an excellent opportunity to share experience and knowledge on strategies and measures to combat poverty and promote inclusion across Europe, says the Minister of Labour, Hanne Bjurstrøm.</p>
                
                
